DialogueNode.dialogue: Hi, I'm Alex, the new HR employee!
Oh... cool! I'm Janet. It's nice to meet you.
It's nice to meet you Janet. So what's your role here at Big Byte?
Oh, you know, kinda everything. I guess you could call me a creative.
Cool! I'd consider myself pretty creative too.
If it functions and looks pretty, I had something to do with it... Whether you hear about it or not.
That's... not exactly what I meant. Basically, if it functions and looks pretty, I had something to do with it!
What do you mean by "whether you hear about it or not"?
That sounds awesome! I'm excited to learn more about what you do.
Let's just say, my work isn't always appreciated. But this company needs me more than know.
But that's a story for another day. I really should be getting back to work. It was great to meet you, Alex!
Yeah, I'd love to get to know you more! Though I should really be getting back to work. Let's talk later!
